<i>Melewati kedalaman 3.000 kaki.</i>

30
00:02:31,525 --> 00:02:32,984
<i>Terus menurun.</i>

31
00:02:34,528 --> 00:02:37,531
<i>Akan tetap di sisi utara sejauh ini.</i>

32
