00:02:49,376 --> 00:02:51,044
<i>Sekitar 500 kaki lagi.</i>

34
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,341
<i>BOP terlihat.</i>

35
00:02:56,967 --> 00:03:00,429
PENCEGAH LEDAKAN

36
00:03:00,512 --> 00:03:04,266
PENGAMAN DAN KENDALI TEKANAN SUMUR

37
00:03:04,349 --> 00:03:08,603
KEDALAMAN PENGEBORAN 5.6 KM

38
00:03:10,313 --> 00:03:12,482
<i>Bagaimana kelihatannya di permukaan?</i>

39
00:03:12,983 --> 00:03:17,154
<i>Sedikit karat.
