00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,739
Hei, kau tahu kata sandinya, 'kan?
Di mana dokumen asuransi.

152
00:10:16,823 --> 00:10:17,991
Kau tahu hubungi Schuman dulu.

153
00:10:18,575 --> 00:10:20,451
- Apa maksudmu?
- Aku

154
00:10:21,369 --> 00:10:25,039
- Apa yang kau cemaskan?
- takut naik helikopter sebelumnya.

155
00:10:25,123 --> 00:10:26,708
- Berikan padaku.
- Sayang.

156
00:10:26,791 --> 00:10:30,086
Satu-satunya kau mengkhawatirkan Marinir
adalah saat mereka berhenti bercanda.

157
00:10:30,170 --> 00:10:32,380
- Jangan gunakan kalimatku.
- Sudah.

158
00:10:32,463 --> 00:10:34,465
- Jangan gunakan kalimatku.
- Terlambat.

159
00:10:34,549 --> 00:10:37,051
PELABUHAN FOURCHON

160
00:11:00,241 --> 00:11:05,663
LAPANGAN HELIKOPTER BRISTOW

161
00:11:10,543 --> 00:11:11,753
Baiklah, Sayang.

162
00:11:11,836 --> 00:11:12,921
Baiklah, Fish.

163
00:11:14,047 --> 00:11:16,007
- Aku mencintaimu.
- Aku juga.

164
00:11:17,133 --> 00:11:20,053
- Sampai jumpa dalam tiga pekan.
- Baiklah.

165
00:11:20,136 --> 00:11:21,179
Jaga dirimu.

166
00:11:23,973 --> 00:11:24,891
Berikutnya.

167
00:11:25,391 --> 00:11:26,935
Selamat pagi, Pak Jimmy.

168
00:11:27,018 --> 00:11:28,061
- Apa kabar, Sarah?
- Baik.

169
00:11:28,144 --> 00:11:29,187
- Kau?
- Baik.

170
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:32,148
Letakkan ranselmu di timbangan
dan berdiri di atas tanda.

171
00:11:32,649 --> 00:11:33,691
Ke mana tujuanmu hari ini?

172
00:11:33,775 --> 00:11:35,068
Tempat yang sama. Deepwater Horizon.

173
00:11:35,151 --> 00:11:36,027
Kau mau ke mana?

174
00:11:36,110 --> 00:11:38,071
- Deepwater Horizon.
- Kau bekerja untuk siapa?

175
00:11:38,154 --> 00:11:39,072
Transocean.

176
00:11:39,155 --> 00:11:41,157
- Kau ingin tahu berapa berat badanmu?
- Tentu saja.

177
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,909
- 90 kg.
- Apa kubilang?

178
00:11:42,992 --> 00:11:45,119
- Ya, kerja bagus. Pertahankan.
- Baiklah.

179
00:11:45,203 --> 00:11:47,622
Baiklah. Silakan tunggu di lobi, akan
kami panggil saat penerbangan siap.

180
00:11:47,705 --> 00:11:49,415
- Terima kasih.
- Pak Sims?

181
00:11:49,499 --> 00:11:50,416
Pak O'Bryan?

182
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,584
David Sims.

183
00:11:51,668 --> 00:11:54,420
Aku Jimmy Harrell. Manajer Instalasi
Lepas Pantai di Deepwater.

184
00:11:54,504 --> 00:11:56,965
Sobat, terima kasih
telah mengantar kami hari ini.

185
00:11:57,048 --> 00:11:59,550
Aku tahu kalian kewalahan
dan tak perlu berterima kasih.

186
00:11:59,634 --> 00:12:00,677
Tidak, aku harus berterima kasih.

187
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,637
Dengar, bisa lepaskan dasinya?

188
00:12:03,346 --> 00:12:04,931
Kurasa tidak.

189
00:12:05,014 --> 00:12:07,558
Bukan soal dasinya. Tapi warnanya.

190
00:12:07,642 --> 00:12:08,601
Ungu?

191
00:12:09,435 --> 00:12:10,853
Lebih mirip magenta.

192
00:12:11,938 --> 00:12:12,772
Dan?

193
00:12:12,855 --> 00:12:16,776
Alarm warna magenta di kilang
adalah yang terburuk.

194
00:12:17,402 --> 00:12:19,362
Itu menyebabkan trauma.

195
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:21,864
Selamat pagi.

196
00:12:21,948 --> 00:12:23,241
Mike Williams.

197
00:12:23,324 --> 00:12:24,993
- Ke mana tujuanmu hari ini?
- Deepwater Horizon.

198
00:12:26,744 --> 00:12:27,870
Baiklah.

199
00:12:42,385 --> 00:12:43,761
Apa aktivitasmu saat libur?

200
00:12:44,554 --> 00:12:46,889
Aku mulai mengerjakan
perahu baling-baling itu lagi.

201
00:12:46,973 --> 00:12:47,807
Benarkah?

202
00:12:47,890 --> 00:12:51,394
Kutingkatkan dari 600 DK ke 1.200 DK.

203
00:12:52,186 --> 00:12:55,982
Dan kupasang baling-baling
Sensenich dari Super Cub.

204
00:12:56,065 --> 00:12:57,400
Kau ingin menerbangkannya?

205
00:12:57,483 --> 00:12:59,444
Tidak, aku hanya ingin
menjadikannya lebih cepat.

206
00:13:06,951 --> 00:13:07,827
Diterima.

207
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,662
<i>Dimengerti. Semua penumpang telah naik.</i>

208
00:13:09,746 --> 00:13:12,915
<i>Hei, Boscow, kudapat koordinat
Deepwater Horizon di FMS.</i>

209
00:13:13,499 --> 00:13:16,044
<i>492, tak ada halangan. Angin tenang.</i>

210
00:13:16,127 --> 00:13:18,880
<i>Landas pacu 21 sedang digunakan.
Altimeter 2997.</i>

211
00:13:41,235 --> 00:13:43,946
<i>Paris Control, ini Bristow 2 Bravo Gulf.</i>

212
00:13:44,030 --> 00:13:45,698
<i>Kami menuju laut lepas.</i>

213
00:13:45,782 --> 00:13:48,367
<i>Perkiraan tiba 45 menit
menuju Deepwater Horizon.</i>

214
00:13:49,118 --> 00:13:51,287
<i>Dimengerti, Bristow 2 Bravo Gulf.</i>

215
00:13:51,370 --> 00:13:53,915
Apa yang kau kerjakan di BP, Pak Sims?

216
00:13:53,998 --> 00:13:55,291
Studi kelayakan.

217
00:13:55,374 --> 00:13:56,626
Sial, ini dia, Jimmy.

218
00:13:56,709 --> 00:13:59,337
Seperti yang kau tahu,
kami agak terlambat.

219
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:02,048
Sudah 43 hari.
