1438
01:28:15,914 --> 01:28:17,749
Shane Albers!

1439
01:28:17,832 --> 01:28:18,750
Di sini!

1440
01:28:20,001 --> 01:28:22,087
Caleb Holloway!

1441
01:28:22,170 --> 01:28:23,171
Di sini!

1442
01:28:27,008 --> 01:28:28,844
Jason Anderson!

1443
01:28:31,763 --> 01:28:34,182
Jason Anderson, kau ada di sini?

1444
01:28:37,686 --> 01:28:40,438
