01:29:07,716 --> 01:29:09,134
Dewey Revette?

1448
01:29:13,138 --> 01:29:14,681
Shane Roshto?

1449
01:29:16,766 --> 01:29:18,184
Adam Weise?

1450
01:29:23,940 --> 01:29:25,191
Roy Kemp?

1451
01:29:26,818 --> 01:29:29,529
Kami memiliki ruang medis
di geladak atas, ya?

1452
01:29:30,822 --> 01:29:32,365
Dale Burkeen?

1453
01:29:37,454 --> 01:29:38,830
Gordon Jones?

1454
01:29:42,751 --> 01:29:44,502
Karl Kleppinger?

1455
01:29:52,093 --> 01:29:53,511
Stephen Curtis?

